OL,4,Cfollowing sexual harassment by male
OL,5,Cboss
OL,7,FA Northern Ireland woman has settled a
OL,8,Fsexual harassment case against a
OL,9,Fformer employer after being "slapped
OL,10,Fon the bottom" by a male supervisor.
OL,12,FJayla Boyd settled her case against
OL,13,Fher former employer JD Sports Fashion
OL,14,FPLC for #65,000.
OL,16,FThe company acknowledged and
OL,17,Fapologised for the significant upset,
OL,18,Fdistress, and injury to feelings
OL,19,Fexperienced by Ms Boyd.
