OL,7,FShe had worked part-time at a Belfast
OL,8,Fstore while studying for her A-levels.
OL,10,FIt was during this time she said she
OL,11,Fwas slapped on the bottom by a male
OL,12,Fsupervisor.
OL,14,FMs Boyd said she reported the incident
OL,15,Fto her manager that day and was told
OL,16,Fthat CCTV had captured the incident.
OL,17,FHowever, the supervisor was allowed to
OL,18,Fcontinue to work alongside her for the
OL,19,Frest of the shift.
