OL,7,FChief commissioner Geraldine McGahey
OL,8,Fsaid employers should have clear
OL,9,Fpolicies and procedures in place to
OL,10,Fdeal with harassment."A zero-tolerance
OL,11,Fapproach by employers to sexual
OL,12,Fharassment in the workplace will
OL,13,Fremind everyone how seriously it will
OL,14,Fbe dealt with should any instances
OL,15,Farise," she said.
OL,17,F"In order to prevent it, employers
OL,18,Fmust ensure that all staff know what
OL,19,Fbehaviour is acceptable, and
OL,20,Funacceptable, in the workplace.
